# Accessibility and SEO

- Prefer semantic HTML; add ARIA when native elements are not enough.
- Ensure keyboard access and visible focus for interactive controls.
- Use [`BaseLayout.astro`](mdc:src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro) and [`BaseHead.astro`](mdc:src/components/BaseHead.astro) for titles, descriptions, canonical URLs, Open Graph, and optional `robots`.
